{
  "title": "Mustardy Algerian Lamb Tagine",
  "description": "A hearty and flavorful North African stew made with lamb, mustard, and sultanas, served on a hot stone plate. This dish is macrobiotic-friendly and features score-fat for added richness.",
  "cuisine": "Algerian",
